quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  68,34,Toto bwene balia abaria Nyasaye wabu baliba nende emikunda chobwokholo
  68,35,"Ne, khwakhakhola abasalamu shinga aboononi"
  68,36,Mukhabeele murie? mubusinjia murie
  68,37,"Nohomba\tmulineshitabu shiamusomanga mwo"
  68,38,Mbu mulanyoolamwo akamwayanza
  68,39,"Nohomba muli nebitsubo khwifwe, ebiliboosia khu inyanga yeyindukho, mbu toto bwene mulinyoola koosi pe kamubusinjia"
  68,40,"Barebe mbu: “ni wina mubo Omwimilisi wakano"
  68,41,Nohomba bali nende abasaanji ? mana babarere nikali mbu baboolanga akatoto
  68,42,"Inyanga lwomuluku kulifunulwa, nebalilangwa okhwinamila Nyasaye, neshibalinyalilwa tawe"
  68,43,"Tsimoni tsiabu tsilihenga hasi, tsisoni tsilibalia toto bwene balaangungwa okhwinamila Nyasaye ( nibali khushialo) nibali abalamu"
  68,44,"Ndeshela balia bafukula likhuwa lino, khulabasitilia eshinyasio kalahakalaha munjila yabalamanyile tawe"
  68,45,"Ne ndalabahelesia ebise, amaraba kanje ni amasiro"
  68,46,Nohomba ebasabanga omurungo nabo bashilungwa eshichelo esho
  68,47,Nohoma bali nende kefisa kabahandikanga
  68,48,"Linda shinga Nyasaye wuwo yetsa okhubusia, ne olaba shinga omundu weyimonye, olwayalaanga nafwinyiikhe"
  68,49,"Tsikhanyanga okhumuulila tsimbabaasi okhurula khu Nyasaye wuwe, yakhasalilwe khulukuku nafunanibwa"
  68,50,"Halali Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi namwawula , namukhola okhuba mubandu abalayi"
  68,51,"Ne abakhayi hambi hatiti bakhukwisie khulwe tsimoni tsiabu, olwabawulilanga ametsulisio ka-Nyasaye. Nibaboolanga mbu: “ toto bwene ye ni omulalu.”"
  68,52,Ne amakhuwa kano (Ikurani) shikali halali ni ametsulisio khubiloonje bioosi